name: Leiomyosarcoma Ribbon
description: I have leiomyosarcoma a rare form of cancer. I'm doing this to try to raise awareness and support for Leiomyosarcoma research and to help me raise money for my cancer meds and treatments. 50% of all funds raised will be donated to the Sarcoma Foundation of America to aid research to find a cure. Thank you so much for your support.
